iIt wasn't until 1998 that I started writing a blog online. I was		gopher.black	70
ioff to college and learning how to do all this crazy web stuff.		gopher.black	70
iI kept text notes on that website for a while (lost now even to		gopher.black	70
ithe wayback machine, sadly). I later moved to livejournal and kept		gopher.black	70
ia pretty decent journal there with a ring of friends. Thankfully		gopher.black	70
iI harvested some of those old posts before nuking my livejournal		gopher.black	70
iaccount years later. Those earliest posts on my blog now were		gopher.black	70
iwritten there. They've been updated a few times to move to		gopher.black	70
iwordpress, jekyll, and now hugo. I keep that stuff in git now,		gopher.black	70
itoo. Better peace of mind, for sure.		gopher.black	70
